{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":1,"day":11}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"永远忠于党","authors":["解正艺"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我嘴里喊出的第一句话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是妈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心里喊出的第一句话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈和党——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我生命的两个亲娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈教给我的第一支歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是“睡吧！睡着了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会肚子饿。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党教给我的第一支歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是“起来，饥寒交迫的奴隶！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哺我身体的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是妈的奶液；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哺我心灵的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是党的真理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了妈的奶液，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有党的真理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就等于只有生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有生命的意义。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“永远忠于党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一切献给党！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是我一切语言中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最真挚的语言；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“永远忠于党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一切献给党！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是我一切信念中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最崇高的信念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远忠于党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一切献给党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就象生命的种子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投入了肥沃的土壤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根儿向地里深扎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花儿朝太阳开放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕狂风暴雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕严寒冰霜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年果实累累，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命永葆芬芳！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}